<div><head>《沈約晉書》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a.2">元帝</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a.3">琅琊國姓牛者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a.4">與夏侯妃私通，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a.5">生中宗。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a.6">《史通》、《後魏書》及採撰。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a.7">周顗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a.8">王敦素憚之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a.9">輒面熱，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a.10">雖復臘月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a.11">亦扇面不休，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-1a.12">其憚如此。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-2a.2">《世說》注五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-2a.3">王羲之在會稽山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-2a.4">見一老姥持十許六角竹扇。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-2a.5">羲之因書扇，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-2a.6">各作五字。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-2a.7">語姥云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-2a.8">「道是王右軍書，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-2a.9">字索百錢。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-3a.2">《初學記》二十五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-3a.3">裴瓚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-3a.4">字國寶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-3a.5">以風神高邁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-3a.6">為中書郎。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-3a.7">出入禁門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-3a.8">見者皆肅然改容。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-4a.2">《類聚》四十八、《書鈔》五十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-4a.3">康僧淵有義學。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1289_CHANT_001-4a.4">《世說》注二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
